</div>
<br>
上周日，访问路透社点击阅读一篇<a target="_blank" href="http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/06/22/us-israel-syria-border-idUSKBN0EX0CR20140622"><u>以色列指控叙利亚杀死该国一名儿童</u></a>的报道的用户会<a href="https://medium.com/@FredericJacobs/the-reuters-compromise-by-the-syrian-electronic-army-6bf570e1a85b"><u>被定向到</u></a><br>
